title: 2020.02.26 - Prompted Introspection: Vidya Behavior

!! Can television (or videogames) influence your behaviour? How?

Yes. By modifying our beliefs (including just the memory of the experience) or desires, directly or indirectly, thus changing the odds that we might mindlessly behave or choose to behave in particular ways. Obviously, these tools can be used for great evil, but they can also be used wisely. 